}
```

## Early access: Retrieve all line item metadata in a model

**Note:**This is an early access endpoint and is not generally available yet.

Use this call to get all line Items and metadata for a model.

### Request

`curl -X GET 'https://api.anaplan.com/2/0/models/{modelId}/lineItems?includeAll=true' \`  
`-H 'Authorization: AnaplanAuthToken {anaplan_auth_token}' \`  
`-H 'Accept: application/json'`

### Request Headers

| **Header** | **Details** |
| --- | --- |
| `Authorization: AnaplanAuthToken {anaplan_auth_token}` | <br><br>*   Required<br>*   Description: the Anaplan authentication token<br><br> |
| `Accept: application/json` | <br><br>*   Optional<br>*   Description: This call uses a content type of `application/json`.<br><br> |

### Request parameters

| **Parameter** | **Details** |
