| `{modelId}` | <br><br>*   Type: String<br>*   Description: the model ID<br>*   Example: `75A40874E6B64FA3AE0743278996850F`<br><br> |
| `includeAll` | <br><br>*   Required<br>*   Type: boolean<br>*   Description: true or false<br>*   Example: `includeAll=true`<br><br> |

